'''傑夫·強斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Geoff Johns'''}}，{{bd|1973年|1月25日}}）<ref>{{cite web|last=Miller|first=John Jackson|authorlink=John Jackson Miller|url=http://cbgxtra.com/knowledge-base/for-your-reference/comics-industry-birthdays|title=Comics Industry Birthdays|work=[[Comics_Buyer's_Guide|Comics Buyer's Guide]]|date=2005-06-10|location=Iola, Wisconsin|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5trAbNQWw?url=http://cbgxtra.com/knowledge-base/for-your-reference/comics-industry-birthdays|archivedate=2010-10-30|deadurl=yes|accessdate=2016-08-17}}</ref>是一名[[美國|美國]]漫畫男編劇、電影與電視製片人。於2010年至2018年間擔任[[DC漫畫|DC娛樂]]的[[首席创意官|首席創意官]]，2016年5月兼任總裁一職；1999年以來，他已參與過許多DC漫畫角色的作品<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Day_of_Judgment_(comics) |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-10-13 |archive-date=2020-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200406200011/https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Day_of_Judgment_(comics) |dead-url=no }}</ref>，包括[[綠燈俠|綠燈俠]]、[[水行俠|水行俠]]、[[閃電俠|閃電俠]]和[[超人|超人]]。強斯也是名[[漫畫店|漫畫零售商]]<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=21559|title= ReTales|first= Jud|last= Meyers|date= 2009-06-06|publisher= [[Comic_Book_Resources|Comic Book Resources]]|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140408042017/http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=21559|archivedate= 2014-04-08|deadurl= no|accessdate= 2016-08-17}}</ref>。

2016年5月起，他和[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]的執行副總裁強·柏格共同擔任[[DC影業|DC影業]]的主導者<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.vulture.com/2016/05/geoff-johns-dc-films.html?mid=twitter_vulture|title=The New Co-Chief of DC Superhero Movies Is Big On Hope and Optimism|last=Riesman|first=Abraham|work=Vulture|date=2016-05-18|accessdate=2016-05-27|archive-date=2016-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160521041242/http://www.vulture.com/2016/05/geoff-johns-dc-films.html?mid=twitter_vulture|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在《[[正義聯盟_(電影)|正義聯盟]]》起的[[DC擴展宇宙|DC擴展宇宙]]電影擔任監製，2018年6月辭去相關職務，改以編劇和製片人形式參與之後相關內容。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Geoff Johns Exits DC Entertainment for Writing and Producing Deal (Exclusive) {{!}} Hollywood Reporter|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/geoff-johns-exits-dc-entertainment-writing-producing-deal-1118131|accessdate=2020-09-17|work=www.hollywoodreporter.com|archive-date=2018-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180728224401/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/geoff-johns-exits-dc-entertainment-writing-producing-deal-1118131|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Geoff Johns辞去DC漫画CCO，专注撰写《绿灯剧团》剧本|url=http://www.sohu.com/a/235650191_99907258|accessdate=2020-09-17|work=www.sohu.com|language=en}}</ref>

==個人生活==
強斯住在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]<ref>Rogers, Vaneta; [[Biggers,_Cliff|Biggers, Cliff]] (September 2008). "Planet Stories" ''[[Comic_Shop_News|Comic Shop News]]'' #1108.</ref>。他的妹妹寇特妮（Courtney）是[[環球航空800號班機空難|環球航空800號班機空難]]的受害者。DC漫畫角色{{link-en|寇特妮·惠特莫爾|Courtney Whitmore}}就是強斯參考自妹妹<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.newsarama.com/2816-best-shots-legion-wonderland-literals-and-more.html|title= Best Shots: ''Legion'', ''Wonderland'', ''Literals'' and More|first= Troy|last= Brownfield|date= 2009-05-08|publisher= Newsarama|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140417005236/http://www.newsarama.com/2816-best-shots-legion-wonderland-literals-and-more.html|archivedate= 2014-04-17|deadurl= no|accessdate= 2016-08-17}}</ref>。

